"
    The example demonstrates how a views visibility can be toggled
    while being in a panel (the geometry of the other view is automatically adjusted).

    [author:]
        Claus Gittinger

    [see also:]
        GUIDemoVisibility

    [start with:]
        GUIDemoVisibilityToggleInPanel open
        GUIDemo open
"
! !

